body:
In case you haven't heard, there's this nifty lil' thing called The Hunger Games simulator where you can generate your own hunger games match between people of your choice. The outcomes can be pretty funny and relatable, so why not make an Avicus version of it?
Here is the link to it.
EDIT: Nevermind, the link's being stubborn.

Just comment below if you want to be involved in it. I'll generate more than one round if more than 24 people want to enter. ;>

FIRST 24 PEOPLE (Please excuse the incorrect genders. District members were also randomly generated):
http://pastebin.com/qzrsKAYC

SECOND 24 PEOPLE (Same as above):
http://pastebin.com/eXg3CCuD
